### 1. Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}

### 2. Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{USER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}

### 3. Update User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{USER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Jane Doe Updated",
  "email": "jane.updated@example.com",
  "profilePicture": "https://example.com/profile.jpg"
}

### 4. Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{USER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}

